issue.title: `:php:method:` links not working.
issue.body: Perhaps I'm doing something wrong here, but I can't seem to get method links to work in my guides. I've tried a number of different styles, but none of them seem to work at all: ```rst :php:method:`\Application\Utilities\File::locateFile()` :php:method:`Application\Utilities\File::locateFile()` :php:method:`\Application\Utilities\File::locateFile` ``` All of these result in `` being inserted into the output HTML. The same is true for any method link anywhere in my guides. I've verified that there are no misspellings in the names. I'm using phpDocumentor v3.4.3.
